#: ../../tips_and_tricks/useful_info/color_hell.rst:40
msgid ""
"From time to time, you may get into weird digital video territory quite "
"unexpectedly. For instance, you just want to cut some screen records made on "
"mobile devices, such as tablets or mobile phones, only to find out that "
"something is wrong with the colors."
msgstr ""
"De tant en tant, es pot entrar en un territori estrany del vídeo digital de "
"manera inesperada. Per exemple, només voleu retallar alguns enregistraments "
"de pantalla fets en dispositius mòbils, com ara tauletes o telèfons mòbils, "
"només per a descobrir que alguna cosa no ha anat bé amb els colors."

